        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">About Me</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">I am a data-focused student passionate about turning raw data into clear, actionable business insights.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Strong data processing & machine learning skills</li>
            <li>Experience in NLP, classification tasks, and visualization</li>
