        <div class="border p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Fake News Detection Using Machine Learning & Deep Learning</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Apr 2026</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700">
                <li>Built classification models to identify real vs fake news</li>
                <li>Compared LR, NB, Random Forest, MLP, DistilBERT</li>
                <li>Dataset: 40,000 labeled news articles</li>
                <li>Best model: PyTorch MLP with 95% accuracy & F1-score</li>
                <li>Optimized batch size, learning rate, and loss function</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline mt-3 inline-block">View Code →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

